": ["1921-01-26"], "description": ["W Sit ij r I1 i 9 a t I I 1 t J I a I r Mr and Mrs Pete Nelson of Morris township were in the city Monday ValentinesGet them at Slorby Bergs cl26 Mrs Gust Fjelseth spent last week in Fargo visiting friends and relatives F Bullock of Knox transacted bus iness in the city the first of the week William Guy attended the Grain Growers meeting in Fargo last week George Kline and R Steinke farm ers of the Penn district were in the city Monday R E Nelson of Morris township was a visitor at county treasurer Powells office Monday Mrs Ray Trowbridge returned Tues day from Southam where she spent the past two weeks visiting friends Albert Thompson and Gust Mad sen of Brocket were in the city Mon day attending to business matters Mildred Getts daughter of Mr and Mrs Irvin Getts is confined to her home on Uline avenue with chicken pox Warren Dodge of Fargo is in the city fostering general science lectures at the high school for teachers and pupils Cordwood 1000 sawed 12 delivered posts 15c to 25c Special prices on quantities in woods W B Smith Phone"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-08-25T19:28:34.530Z", "group": ["ndnp/ndhi", "state-histrorical-society-of-north-dakota-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn88076526/1921-01-26/ed-1/?sp=12", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ndhi:batch_ndhi_isley_ver01:data:sn88076526:00295863869:1921012601:0549/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=275&w=228", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ndhi:batch_ndhi_isley_ver01:data:sn88076526:00295863869:1921012601:0549/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=550&w=456", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ndhi:batch_ndhi_isley_ver01:data:sn88076526:00295863869:1921012601:0549/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1101&w=913", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ndhi/batch_ndhi_isley_ver01/data/sn88076526/00295863869/192101260